g.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/3d7e4d9b9ea5fbcf1cc2c0fa1f05fffd-kix.jf7a4ahbbq7d-1024x630.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/3d7e4d9b9ea5fbcf1cc2c0fa1f05fffd-kix.jf7a4ahbbq7d-1024x630.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/3d7e4d9b9ea5fbcf1cc2c0fa1f05fffd-kix.jf7a4ahbbq7d-300x185.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/3d7e4d9b9ea5fbcf1cc2c0fa1f05fffd-kix.jf7a4ahbbq7d-768x472.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/3d7e4d9b9ea5fbcf1cc2c0fa1f05fffd-kix.jf7a4ahbbq7d-jpg.webp 1200w" width="1024" height="630" /></a></p><p>招聘期限：永久</p><p>男性VTuber团体“ <a href="https://www.holostars.tv/bosyu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Holostars</a> ”一直在寻找人才。招聘要求与上述Hololive相同。</p><p><a href="https://audition.hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>查看特别试镜页面。</p><h2 id="link18">如何通过试镜？</h2><p>正如我们所介绍的，VTuber试镜的选择标准根据公司的不同而有所不同，重要的是你想要做的公司的理念以及公司的理念或者是否符合企业试镜条件。</p><p>除此之外，还需要歌唱、舞蹈、语言、游戏、谈话等多种能力。最近，对语言能力特别感兴趣的公司越来越多，如果你能用英语和中文与粉丝交谈，你往往会支持试镜。 </p><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2022/01/202201021118082000-300x169.jpg"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weight-normal">如果我想成为vtuber我该怎么办？需要了解的内容、注意事项等基础知识汇总</h3><div class="text-gray mg-mogura-card-excerpt mb-1 my-md-2">很多人看着每天活跃的Vtuber的直播和视频，就会想：“我也想做！”不过，我能做的事情还有很多，首先需要的东西，我也不太了解，所以还早……</div> <span class="badge badge-outline-live mg-mogura-card-badge px-2">VTuber</span> <span class="text-muted small ml-1">2022.01.02</span></div></div></div><p>例如，在热门VTuber团体“Nijisanji”的试镜中，活跃的Vtuber <a href="https://twitter.com/Nui_Sociere" target="_blank" r