入，例如移动运动捕获“ <a href="https://www.sony.jp/mocopi/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">mocopi</a> ”，带有键盘的步行运动和选定的动画。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="[House 3D凸面等待] Poko Mari失去了Mocopi [Holo Live/Treasure Marine/Rabo​​ta Pokora]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ym83gIIc7vs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe><br /> （实际使用多个跟踪输入的分发）</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-jpg.webp 800w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/1dfcca1ea53f74a4e9641a8b05831b39-kix.55860jpwpqjm-768x432.webp 768w" width="800" height="450" /></a></p><p>此外，在计算类人生物模型的姿势时，详细介绍了统一的特殊情况。尽管它仅适用于工程师，但它不仅是由一个系统或设备建立的，而且由于多个技术集成，它已经实现了。</p><p>单击此处以获取官方注释的详细信息。<br /> <a href="https://note.cover-corp.com/n/n7a413a4c167b" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://note.cover-corp.com/n/n7a413a4c167b</a></p><p> Cover Co.，Ltd。一直在积极介绍上述技术介绍。看来这是针对感兴趣领域的工程师的招募，但是对整个VTUBER行业的贡献是由很少在前阶段揭示的专业技术部件公开宣传的。它似乎已连接。到。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://note.cover-corp.com/n/n7a413a4c167b" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方注释</a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/hololive-3d-live-behind-the-scenes/">Horo Live的“ House 3D发行版”如何实现？封面引入了跟踪技术的背面，</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ;
有没有像这样的音乐形式？一种虚拟和真实的融合，被透明的LED“ double：”体验报告所迷住https://www.moguravr.com/double-报道/けいろー Wed, 31 Jan 2024 09:55:06 +0000 VTuberActiv8 https://www.moguravr.com/?p=244919 <p> 2024年1月26日。活动“ Double：”称为“混合音乐节”，在Ikebukuro Harevutai举行了真实和虚拟相交的活动。由Activ8赞助。这是一家创造Kizuna Eye的公司[…]</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/double-report/">那里的帖子是如此的音乐现场形状，而虚拟和真实的“ double：trial回购”的融合</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p> 2024年1月26日。活动`` <strong>Double：</strong> &#39;&#39;，被称为``一个混合音乐节，在ikebukuro Harevutai举行了真正的和虚拟的相交&#39;。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.h1qubtedmi7m-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>由<a href="https://activ8.co.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Activ8</a>赞助。虽然它是创建Kizuna AI的公司，但近年来，它还创建了一个3DCG的UTA模型，该模型出现在“一部电影Red”中，支持了“ Project im@svα-liv”的生产，并且他在Vrchat举办了活动。他参与了虚拟现场表演“ Metropulse”胶囊现场表演的现场演出。</p><p>此事件由Activ8主持。它最大的功能是<strong>结合虚拟和真实的混合产生</strong>。预先通知强调，它将利用“包括尖端透明LED在内的数字技术”，这表明这是一种与典型的VTUBER音乐现场不同的新尝试。</p><p>实际上，表演艺术家的阵容也是独一无二的。一位在2D和3D工作的歌手，以及在音乐以外的其他领域吸引注意力的创作者。 DJ和音乐制作人在角色项目中活跃于以舞蹈音乐为主题的角色项目中。感觉就像他们正在扮演不同背景的艺术家，并且在广义上是由``表达&#39;&#39;激励的。</p><p>四位具有不同标题和流派的艺术家将在Activ8举办的活动中演出，该活动却产生了许多虚拟现场表演。如果是这样，我相信我们会看到一些新作品和有趣的表达方式。在本文中，我们将向您介绍“ Double：”的期望如此备受期望。</p><h2>最先进的透明LED显示显示，该显示清晰，生动地投射图像</h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="双：第1卷预告电影" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zvgWiVo5vGA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “ Double：”有四位艺术家唱歌和表演近两个半小时，并在全面的现场剧院中挤满了观众。</p><p>我对整个现场表演的印象可以用一个词来概括：` <strong>`我觉得“虚拟”表达方法的扩展性和Vtuber音乐的潜力是真实的“体验”。”</strong>当然，主要的前提是这是一场非常愉快的音乐现场表演。</p><p>最让我印象深刻的是``<strong>最先进的透明LED&#39;&#39;的存在，</strong>这是在预先通知中提到的。实际上，说这些透明的LED是现场表演的关键，这并不夸张。</p><p>首先，请查看下图。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.b69ykdchfkkm-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>你明白吗？图片看起来像是三个元素的组合：虚拟效果（漩涡），真实表演者（Daoko）和背景图像（浅蓝色的风景）。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8ckgfe4ewwi-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>此外，在上面的图像中，虚拟Yuka nagase在真正的Yuka Nagase前面透明地出现。这到底是什么意思？</p><p>首先，在现实世界中的一般现场音乐场所举行的``Vtuber Music Live&#39;&#39;上，将VTubers的图像投影到舞台上设置的大型展示上。尽管在大规模音乐会（例如Nijisanji and Hololive）以及瓦萨比音乐学校的真人大小的头像现场系统等大型音乐会中经常看到AR效果，但````展示&#39;&#39;&#39;风格是小型到小型的主流。中型活动。你可以这么说。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-jpg.webp 960w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.8k4bfgslkbsw-768x432.webp 768w" width="960" height="540" /></a><br /> （一般的中型Vtuber Live。如果有真实的表演者，他们通常会出现在屏幕前面）</p><p>这次是“ Double：”也以类似的风格投射了VTuber，但与过去有一些差异。<strong>舞台背景安装了一个全尺度的LED高清显示屏，除此之外，在观众座椅附近的舞台上还有另一个大型透明的LED显示屏，并在其中显示了VTUBER/角色。正在投影</strong>。</p><p>换句话说，如果将其绘制为图表，则看起来像这样：</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-jpg.webp 960w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.5qokh1phehqt-768x432.webp 768w" width="960" height="540" /></a><br /> （在“双：”的情况下：vtuber出现在透明的LED中，以蓝色显示）</p><p>这种透明LED的透明度是值得注意的。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.gzdtemj3zr4h-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.4luk8qlnxrzc-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p><strong>一旦您知道它在那里，它看起来很正常，但是在表演之前，当显示赞助商镜头时，我不知道显示屏是透明的。</strong>现场表演开始了，来自Minato Shirokane Jogakuin的两个顶级击球手（Kurotetsu Tama和Shirokane Jogakuin）出现在舞台上，当VJ开始在他们身后玩耍时，他们终于说，``我们正在使用两个展示。 。如果我一直在观众的面前，我可能会立即注意到它，但是至少从远处我看不到它。</p><p>一旦我意识到了透明的LED的存在，我就会对所预测的图像的美丽感到惊讶。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.sr2v0u2ys9n6-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.msxqrwu3rwfc-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.l0o2mxicfj9m-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>如果实时展示角色的投射位置，取决于显示的性能，颜色看起来很奇怪，或者您可能会看到闪烁或及时的闪烁。然而，来自墨西哥皇马女子高中的两名学生当天出现在舞台上，不仅明确预测了他们的常规人物，而且即使他们搬家很多，也没有任何不适感或根本不含糊。<strong>精美地描绘了颤抖的头发和衣服下摆的摇摆，甚至明显捕捉了激烈的舞蹈表演的清晰度。</strong></p><p>顺便说一下，除了一些例外，在这个现场表演中允许摄影和录制，但是如果您写作，``即使智能手机相机也可以清楚地捕获投影在透明LED上的数字和动作。&#39;&#39;我是否想知道我是否可以传达只是一点点令人惊奇。实际性能发布在“ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DOUBLE_XR?src=hashtag_click" target="_blank" rel="noopener">#Double_xr</a> ”上，因此，如果您有兴趣，请查看。</p><h2>透明LED和深层真正的X虚拟混合体验扩大了“ Live”表达</h2><p>顺便说一句，正如我在前面图中所述的那样，两个显示器之间是原始的``真实表演者的阶段&#39;&#39;。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-682x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 682px) 100vw, 682px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-682x1024.webp 682w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-200x300.webp 200w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-768x1153.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-1023x1536.webp 1023w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.3lem1vgkc51-jpg.webp 1066w" width="682" height="1024" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.f0y379ciwn7j-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.v6ybh44x4wt9-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>换句话说，<strong>尽管有两个显示，但有三层</strong>。真正的艺术家可以通过在两个显示器之间站立，不仅是大型展示，而且可以在观众身上安装的透明LED来表演。换句话说，它将<strong>虚拟生产带到了“真实”方面</strong>。透明LED的存在不仅对Vtuber，而且对真正的艺术家都是有益的。</p><p> - 这就是我在现场表演的上半年的想法，但是过了一会儿，我意识到还有另一层。在演出期间，通过透明的唱歌唱歌的大科<a href="https://twitter.com/Daok0" target="_blank" rel="noopener">（Daoko）</a>在展示之前就出来了。客观地说，只是``唱歌的艺术家搬到了舞台的前面&#39;&#39; &#39; 也！？&#39;&#39;</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.21j43jmh8cum-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>说到“来到这一方面”，我认为<a href="https://twitter.com/yuka_n_RIOT" target="_blank" rel="noopener">纳加斯</a>的存在和阶段在这个现场中仍然是象征性的，“真实和虚拟的混合”。 <strong>Yuka Nagase出现在虚拟歌手中，很快出现在一位真正的歌手中。</strong>场景包含在Nagase本人发布的Digest视频中，因此请务必查看下面的帖子。令我惊讶的是，它确实立即被切换了。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="ja">操场的舞台只能被任何人困住。</p><p>混合音乐节“ Double：”<br />分销票的出售至今晚20:00，而观看截止日期为止，直到今晚23:59 <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f4e3.png" alt="📣" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p>请把它烧成您的眼睛，XR的新可能性。<br />单击此处购买▼ <a href="https://t.co/7sG8d1YJw8">https://t.co/7sg8d1yjw8</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DOUBLE_XR?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#double_xr_xr</a> <a href="https://t.co/iwl6hB7BhK">pic.twitter.com/iwl6hb7bhk</a></p><p> —Aka Nagase（@yuka_n_riot） <a href="https://twitter.com/yuka_n_RIOT/status/1751853493579808987?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">，2024年1月29日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.qci6jnte440d-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.qci6jnte440d-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.qci6jnte440d-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.qci6jnte440d-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/u