471-kix.o7qonpri5q5x-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.o7qonpri5q5x-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.o7qonpri5q5x-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.o7qonpri5q5x-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.o7qonpri5q5x-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.o7qonpri5q5x-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.c6l5sat7pk6z-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p>另一方面，真正的艺术家的表演并不总是使用透明的LED。因此，当在关键场景中投射三维效果时，您会感觉到图像的独特慢弱和慢跑，就好像突然出现在您的眼前一样。</p><p>一系列使用透明LED的生产可以被视为被称为“ AR”表达式。但是，就个人而言，可能有一种“视觉插孔”的感觉，通常在VR MV中可以看到，并且粒子活着（因为VR不遵循我的头部运动，所以这是一种自然。尽管这是完全不同的事情）。</p><p>另一点是声学非常好，与视觉效果同步并增强了表演的现实主义。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-768x511.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-1536x1022.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.fwcqpxohtvgx-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-1024x682.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-1024x682.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-300x200.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-768x512.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-1536x1023.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.7s75fsnnj2xv-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="682" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/01/6e53137030e10dbaede17ddd45f36471-kix.29ftbk77cnbc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/u